{"tid":1013403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇GUCCI冷衫俾人話種族歧視","createTime":"2019-02-08T10:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T15:45:01.000Z","uid":216523,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"062a9d68d04dcef038a89c2416f35bd2eb5deb0c","tid":1013403,"uid":216523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:12:18.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】意大利名牌GUCCI急忙將一款衣領口可覆蓋着下半邊臉的「黑臉毛衣」下架，並緊急貼出道歉聲明。據報，Gucci推出該款黑色毛衣後，在社交媒體上招致許多批評。<br />\n<br />\n這一款名為Balaclava的高領黑色毛衣的設計，衣領口可覆蓋着下半邊臉，並留有一個切口露出嘴唇，切口旁紅色的周邊呈現出大紅唇效果，對此有部分消費者感到被種族歧視，因為衣服「類似黑臉」，是有對非洲裔美國人的刻板印象，GUCCI隨即在Twitter上被網民們強烈抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n網民Keisha Ka&rsquo;oir貼文表示：「GUCCI今天發表了他們的Balaclava毛衣，嘆，真的是GUCCI？真的？」顯示出不可置信的語氣，而下方也有留言聲援「沒人會買這麼可怕的產品，除非在北極，不然這種設計沒有意義」、「很可恥」、「他們瘋了」。<br />\n<br />\n目前，Gucci發佈聲明稱就任何侵犯行為道歉，並表示將下架該商品。<br />\n<br />\n非裔美國作家邁克爾・邦納（Michael Bonner）在Twitter表示，對於GUCCI這樣一個國際品牌做出這樣的事情，即使快速的道歉並闡明「我不知道」，但對我來說這仍然無法接受。<br />\n<br />\n但網絡上也有網民覺得有人大驚小怪，一位女性網民就留言表示「這件毛衣設計很醜，但它不算歧視，不然滑雪面具也只能用其他顏色是嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n事實上國際名牌引發爭議的例子眾多，近日Prada也因涉嫌種族歧視，下架了一個黑臉紅唇玩偶。<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/gucci%E9%BB%91%E8%87%89%E6%AF%9B%E8%A1%A3%E6%B6%89%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%80%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-042400940.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fgucci%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%2587%2589%25E6%25AF%259B%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2580%25A5%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259E%25B6%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589-042400940.html&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1IeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=261c1569\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/gucci%E9%BB%91%E8%87%89%E6%AF%9B%E8%A1%A3%E6%B6%89%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%80%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89-042400940.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hiPy60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hiPy60.jpg&h=1b31c9d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45c243f92d9c60f8bd4d1451ef75c7db60a74fe2","tid":1013403,"uid":211579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"你慌d niggar 會罷買咩"},{"pid":"b14ec13abdd0e9512ebbb2e00a2e41318dc4a741","tid":1013403,"uid":216523,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"都唔撚明點樣歧視法"},{"pid":"d2d21ec2b652d3977477bceb0244f7ab0a0cf720","tid":1013403,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:21:21.000Z","msg":"Fashion 的野，唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"d4ee2a120ae66eaf9e096c24e84d9ae67347ace3","tid":1013403,"uid":23058,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZOPza5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZOPza5.png&h=70386059&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdc3e17166ad4ea5ad99119a49598db5bae84909","tid":1013403,"uid":7814,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"左膠煩撚到<br />\n咁都叫歧視<br />\n遲d 黑衫黑褲都唔撚比著"},{"pid":"1950ed854be91cff0b7459eadc6ac90fe8cbc463","tid":1013403,"uid":49918,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31b300db9bfdc2c8e2d3c0ca7f74ac870709df77","tid":1013403,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4daf33507d68b2eff8f010e468a18ac20425c97b","tid":1013403,"uid":199417,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:29:04.000Z","msg":"賣黑色衫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你係度消費黑人呀？歧視！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔賣黑色衫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你係咪覺得黑人係低等人種呀而家？歧視！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢鋪真係公你贏字我輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gi